By: Ibrâhîm b. Adham
---
This is the sign of the gnostic, that his thoughts are mostly engaged in
meditation, and his words are mostly praise and glorification of God, and
his deeds are mostly devotion, and his eye is mostly fixed on the subtleties
of Divine action and power.
